name: Jacklyn Hyde
rusAnnotation: We’re going to get older whether we like it or not, so the only question is whether we get on with our lives, or desperately cling to the past.
enAnnotation: If you’re going to call me names, I would prefer Ross, the Divorce Force. It’s just cooler.
